ial Field House\n| site_cityst  = [[Huntington, West Virginia|Huntington, WV]]\n| score        = 69\u201357\n| record       = 22\u20133\n}}\n|-\n!colspan=12 style={{CollegePrimaryStyle|Cincinnati Bearcats}}|[[1961 NCAA University Division Basketball Tournament|<span style={{CollegePrimaryStyle|Cincinnati Bearcats}}>NCAA Tournament </span>]]\n{{CBB schedule entry\n| date         = March 17\n| w/l          = w\n| nonconf      = yes\n| neutral      = yes\n| rank         = 2\n| opponent     = [[1960\u201361 Texas Tech Red Raiders men's basketball team|Texas Tech]]\n| opprank      = \n| site_stadium = [[Allen Fieldhouse]]\n| site_cityst  = [[Lawrence, Kansas|Lawrence, KS]]\n| gamename     = Midwest Region Semifinals\n| score        = 78\u201355\n| record       = 23\u20133\n}}\n{{CBB schedule entry\n| date         = March 18\n| w/l          = w\n| nonconf      = yes\n| neutral      = yes\n| rank         = 2\n| opponent     = {{cbb link|year=1960\u201361|ex=men|team=Kansas State Wildcats|title=Kansas State}}\n| opprank      = 4\n| site_stadium = Allen Fieldhouse\n| site_cityst  = Lawrence, KS\n| gamename     = Midwest Region Finals\n| score        = 69\u201364\n| record       = 24\u20133\n}}\n{{CBB schedule entry\n| date         = March 24\n| w/l          = w\n| nonconf      = yes\n| neutral      = yes\n| rank         = 2\n| opponent     = {{cbb link|year=1960\u201361|ex=men|team=Utah Utes|title=Utah}}\n| opprank      = \n| site_stadium = [[Municipal Auditorium]]\n| site_cityst  = [[Kansas City, Missouri|Kansas City, MO]]\n| gamename     = Final Four\n| score        = 82\u201367\n| record       = 25\u20133\n}}\n{{CBB schedule entry\n| date         = March 25\n| w/l          = w\n| nonconf      = yes\n| neutral      = yes\n| rank         = 2\n| opponent     = [[1960\u201361 Ohio State Buckeyes men's basketball team|Ohio State]]\n| opprank      = 1\n| site_stadium = Municipal Auditorium\n| site_cityst  = Kansas City, MO\n| gamename     = National Championship\n| score       