o |website=Portaldemariahelena.com |language=pt |access-date=25 April 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170425213706/https://www.portaldemariahelena.com.br/noticias/douradina/2017/03/douradinense-completa-117-anos-sendo-uma-das-mulheres-mais-velhas-mundo.html |archive-date=25 April 2017 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://jornalmilenio.com.br/2018/04/17/dona-filo-completou-118-anos-de-vida/|title=Dona Fil\u00f3 completou 118 anos de vida|publisher=}}</ref><ref>https://massanews.com/noticias/plantao/moradora-de-douradina-completa-119-anos-e-pode-ser-a-pessoa-mais-velha-do-mundo-aJLl6.html</ref><ref>https://cruzeirodooeste.portaldacidade.com/noticias/cidade/dona-filo-completa-120-anos-e-e-uma-das-mulheres-mais-velhas-do-mundo-3548</ref>\n|-\n|Jos\u00e9 Delgado Corrales\n|align=center| M\n|10 March 1900\n|{{ayd|1900|3|10}}\n|[[Costa Rica]]\n|10 March 2020\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.teletica.com/185016_hombre-mas-longevo-de-costa-rica-vota-este-domingo-con-casi-118-anos|title=Hombre m\u00e1s longevo de Costa Rica vota este domingo con casi 118 a\u00f1os - Teletica|website=www.teletica.com}}</ref><ref>https://amprensa.com/2019/03/chepito-el-hombre-mas-longevo-de-costa-rica-cumple-119-anos/</ref><ref>https://www.nacion.com/el-pais/chepito-la-persona-mas-longeva-de-costa-rica/HJPNWZAMWZAIZK5THNBSCYUDEE/story/</ref>\n|-\n|Amantina dos Santos Duvirgem \n|align=center|F\n|28 April 1900\n|{{ayd|1900|4|28}}\n|Brazil\n|23 June 2018\n|<ref>[https://tibagi.pr.gov.br/noticias/modules/news/article.php?storyid=7712 Tibagi comemora 117 anos da mulher mais velha do mundo]{{Dead link|date=March 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://arede.info/campos-gerais/219131/dona-julia-completa-118-anos-com-festanca-em-tibagi Dona Julia completa 118 anos]</ref>\n|-\n|Zhu Zhengshi \n|align=center|F\n|21 September 1900\n|{{ayd|1900|9|21}}\n|[[China]]\n|10 Feb 2019\n|<ref>[http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/woman-celebrates-117th-birthday-five-11213764 Woman celebrates 117th birthday with five generations of her family - but she is NOT the oldest in the world]</ref><ref>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/201809/14/WS5b9ae4f6a31033b4f4655f3e_9.html Picture of Zhu Zhengshi at 118]</ref><ref>[https://www.jqknews.com/news/137991-Best_after_00_Born_in_the_family_of_the_Qing_Dynasty_the_old_man_has_lived_together_for_six_generations.html Best after 00! Born in the family of the Qing Dynasty, the old woman has lived together for six generations]</ref>\n|-\n|Aguilar Jaramillo Ignacio\n|align=center| M\n|11 January 1901\n|{{ayd|1901|1|11}}\n|[[Ecuador]]\n|11 January 2020\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://cuencahighlife.com/oldest-man-on-ecuador-maybe-the-world-just-celebrated-his-117th-birthday/|title=Oldest man in Ecuador, maybe the world, just celebrated his 117th birthday \u2013 CuencaHighLife|website=cuencahighlife.com}}</ref><ref>https://www.lahora.com.ec/loja/noticia/1102214172/ignacio-aguilar-jaramillo-nachito-empezo-a-festejar-sus-118-anos</ref><ref>https://www.cronica.com.ec/informacion/item/25880-nachito-cumplio-119-anos-de-vida</ref>\n|-\n|Stephen Wright \n|align=center|M\n|24 August 1901\n|{{ayd|1901|8|24}}\n|[[Jamaica]]\n|26 Aug 2018\n|<ref>[http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/parliament/oldest-living-jamaican-turns-stephen-wright-begging-god-for-at-least-one-more-year_142496 Oldest living Jamaican turns 117] Jamaica Observer</ref>\n|-\n|Masima Leonora Noel\n|align=\"center\" |F\n|9 December 1901\n|{{ayd|1901|12|9}}\n|[[Grenada]]\n|10 December 2018\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pressreader.com/uk/yorkshire-post/20171209/281711204986974|title=Yorkshire family send love to the oldest woman in Commonwealth|access-date=2018-05-13}}</ref>\n|-\n|Dorrisile Dervis\n|align=\"center\" |F\n|25 December 1901\n|{{ayd|1901|12|25}}\n|[[United States]]\n|09 January 2020\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.itemlive.com/2018/03/11/sweet-116-lynn-woman-may-nations-oldest/|title=Sweet 116, Lynn woman may be nation's oldest - Itemlive|date=11 March 2018|website=itemlive.com|accessdate=31 March 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|Sebastiao Batista dos Santos\n|align=center| M\n|15 March 1902\n|{{ayd|1902|3|15}}\n|Brazil\n|05 October 2019\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jornaldebeltrao.com.br/noticia/256988/morador-de-coronel-vivida-completa-115-anos-de-idade |title= Morador de Coronel Vivida completa 115 anos de idade |website= jornaldebeltrao.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.redemaxima.com/Coronel/noticias.php?pg=ver-noticia&id_noticia=2788|title=Sr. Sebasti\u00e3o dos Santos completa 116 anos de idade neste dia 15/03|website=www.redemaxima.com}}</ref><ref>http://www.portalrvp.com.br/ver-noticia/137/seu-sebastiao-batista-dos-santos-completa-117-anos-neste-dia-15-de-marco-de-2019</ref><ref>https://diarioreservense.com.br/noticia/5972/vividense-sebasti-o-batista-dos-santos-o-homem-mais-velho-do-mundo</ref>\n|}\n\n===Past===\nThis table contains supercentenarian claims with either a known death date or no confirmation for more than 2 years that they were still alive. Only claims greater than that of [[Jeanne Calment]] who died at the age of 122 years, 164 days, but under 130 years are included. They are listed in order of age as of the date of death or date last reported alive.\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" width=70%\n!width=30%|Name\n!width=3%|Sex\n!Reported birth date\n!Death date / latest report\n!Reported age\n!width=15%|Country\n|-\n| Ali Ben Mohamed El Amri<ref>{{cite web|url=http://media.daum.net/breakingnews/view.html?cateid=100000&newsid=20100910041808106&fid=20100910041813013&lid=20100910041808106|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20151106062815/http://media.daum.net/breakingnews/view.html?cateid=100000&newsid=20100910041808106&fid=20100910041813013&lid=20100910041808106|url-status=dead|title=TUNISIA OLDEST MAN 130 YEARS OLD - \ub2e4\uc74c\ub274\uc2a4|date=6 November 2015|archivedate=6 November 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://archive.mosaiquefm.net/index/a/