ies in China}}</ref><ref name=\"perfect health\">{{cite news|last=Saatchi|first=Charles|date=10 October 2013|title=Perfect health is merely the slowest way to die|url=http://evening-standard.vlex.co.uk/vid/perfect-is-his-unphotoshopped-looks-468957606|newspaper=London Evening Standard|location=London, UK|publisher=Evening Standard Limited|accessdate=21 November 2013|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203030431/http://evening-standard.vlex.co.uk/vid/perfect-is-his-unphotoshopped-looks-468957606|archivedate=3 December 2013}}</ref>\n |align=center| F\n| 9 July 1885\n| 9 June 2013\n| {{ayd|1885|07|09|2013|06|09}}\n| China\n|-\n| Juana Bautista de la Candelaria Rodr\u00edguez<ref>{{cite web|url=https://mariacelys.wordpress.com/2013/01/10/juana-candelaria-la-mujer-mas-longeva-de-cuba-tenia-al-morir-127-anos|title=Juana Candelaria, la mujer m\u00e1s longeva de #Cuba ten\u00eda al morir 127 a\u00f1os|date=10 January 2013|website=Mariacelys.wordpress.com|accessdate=10 September 2017}}</ref>\n |align=center| F\n| 2 February 1885\n| 24 December 2012\n| {{ayd|1885|2|2|2012|12|24}}\n| Cuba\n|-\n| Luang Pu Chant Siri<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dhammajak.net/forums/viewtopic.php?f=13&t=30195&start=15|title=\u0e41\u0e2a\u0e14\u0e07\u0e01\u0e23\u0e30\u0e17\u0e39\u0e49 - \u0e2b\u0e25\u0e27\u0e07\u0e1b\u0e39\u0e48\u0e2a\u0e35 \u0e09\u0e19\u0e3a\u0e17\u0e2a\u0e34\u0e23\u0e34 \u0e27\u0e31\u0e14\u0e40\u0e02\u0e32\u0e16\u0e49\u0e33\u0e1a\u0e38\u0e0d\u0e19\u0e32\u0e04 \u0e2d\u0e32\u0e22\u0e38 \u0e51\u0e52\u0e58 \u0e1b\u0e35 \u2022 \u0e25\u0e32\u0e19\u0e18\u0e23\u0e23\u0e21\u0e08\u0e31\u0e01\u0e23|website=www.dhammajak.net}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://xn--72c4btmkdhne1gta0c0nxb.com/|title=\u0e2b\u0e25\u0e27\u0e07\u0e1b\u0e39\u0e48\u0e2a\u0e35 \u0e1b\u0e23\u0e30\u0e27\u0e31\u0e15\u0e34\u0e2b\u0e25\u0e27\u0e07\u0e1b\u0e39\u0e48\u0e2a\u0e35 \u0e1e\u0e23\u0e30\u0e40\u0e04\u0e23\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e2b\u0e25\u0e27\u0e07\u0e1b\u0e39\u0e48\u0e2a\u0e35|first=|